==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Optatively
<hw>Op"ta*tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an optative manner; with
the expression of desire.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>God blesseth man imperatively, and man blesseth God
<qex>optatively</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Bp. Hall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Optic</ent>⟦br⟧
